<subSubSection id="C37E65015A7F980BFA9DFB7EE795FAE5" pageId="8" pageNumber="201" type="conservation">
<paragraph id="8BDB368A5A7F980BFA9DFB7EE795FAE5" blockId="8.[1384,2591,851,1392]" pageId="8" pageNumber="201">
<emphasis id="B910EA985A7F980BFA9DFB7EE8D4FB57" bold="true" box="[1386,1745,1245,1274]" pageId="8" pageNumber="201">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red Lust. Provenance of the type specimen of Visagie’s Golden Mole is uncertain, and it has only been seen once (no specimens have been seen or collected since its description).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
